metadata.name: Joby Barrett - “CAPSULE 0”
metadata.description:
CAPSULE 0 is the first edition of the AIMSIR Capsule collection, reflecting on the perception of preservation in the digital age. The collection will be releasing later this year consisting of NFTs, Prints, Sculpture and Jewellery. ‘AIMSIR’ comes from the Proto-Celtic word for ‘time/moment’, this makes the collection is a series of time capsules expressed through a variety of mediums. 

Edition of 150
